===Etymology===
{{compound|en|grape|shot}}, named for the resemblance of the bag of shot to a bunch of grapes.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|grapeshot|s}}

# {{lb|en|historical}} A [[cluster]] of [[small]] [[iron]] [[ball]]s, put together in a [[canvas]] [[bag]] in order to be used as a [[charge]] for a [[cannon]].

